the descent part 2 is a 2009 british adventure horror film and sequel to the 2005 horror film the descent . it was directed by jon harris from a screenplay by james mccarthy , j &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , and james watkins . the film was produced by christian colson and ivana mackinnon ; neil marshall , the writer and director of the original , was an executive producer . shot in london and surrey , it was released in cinemas in the uk on 2 december 2009 and on dvd on 27 april 2010 in the u.s.